        <item>
            <title>Google Speaking Practice 全新 AI 学英文工具，一问一答提升英语会话能力</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/28/google-speaking-practice/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=google-speaking-practice</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/28/google-speaking-practice/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 06:00:39 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Google Speaking Practice]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1231824</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Google 正在其搜寻功能中测试一项名为「口语练习」的新功能，期望能协助用户提升英语会话能力。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1231825 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/gmauzydxgaa3tvx-316x580.jpeg" alt="" width="316" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/gmauzydxgaa3tvx-316x580.jpeg 316w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/gmauzydxgaa3tvx.jpeg 490w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 316px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1231827 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/gmauzx6w4aayrpb-358x580.jpeg" alt="" width="358" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/gmauzx6w4aayrpb-358x580.jpeg 358w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/gmauzx6w4aayrpb.jpeg 556w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 358px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231826" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/gmauzs5wmaa4trh-366x580.jpeg" alt="" width="366" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/gmauzs5wmaa4trh-366x580.jpeg 366w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/gmauzs5wmaa4trh.jpeg 567w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 366px" /></p><p>Google Speaking practice 功能目前向阿根廷、哥伦比亚、印度、印尼、墨西哥及委内瑞拉的英语学习者开放。测试人员可参与由 AI 驱动的互动语言练习，帮助他们在日常情境中使用新单词，从而提升其英语能力。Google 去年 10 月曾推出类似功能，让英语学习者在特定语境中练习发音，并获得有关语法和清晰度的回应。而今次推出的「口语练习」则增加了来回对话练习的难度。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Speaking practice —new AI experiment on Google&#39;s Search Labs! <a href="https://t.co/ZqzyvgXNUZ">pic.twitter.com/ZqzyvgXNUZ</a></p><p>&mdash; ㆅ (@howfxr) <a href="https://twitter.com/howfxr/status/1783448350299214123?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">April 25, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>「口语练习」透过提问一个日常会话问题开始，用户需要以特定单词回答。根据截图显示，一种可能的情境是 AI 告诉用户他们想要变得更健康，然后问道：「我应该怎么办？」用户则需要回答一句包含「exercise」、「heart」及「tired」的话。</p><p>这一新功能表示 Google 可能想同 Duolingo 及 Babbel 等语言学习应用程式作出一番新竞争。虽然这不是 Google 首次涉足语言学习、教育工具，早在 2019 年 Google 就推出过一项功能，让搜寻器用户练习正确发音单词。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://techcrunch.com/2024/04/26/google-improve-english-new-speaking-practice-feature/">TechCrunch</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/28/google-speaking-practice/ai/">Google Speaking Practice 全新 AI 学英文工具，一问一答提升英语会话能力</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/28/google-speaking-practice/ai/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
